M|Lear|Dev |
M|Lear|1. *|** append to MEMORY.md — `[date] — decision — rationale — known risks`
M|Lear|2. *|** add it immediately to the "Rejected Patterns" section in MEMORY.md
M|Lear|3. *|** log the root cause — was it an incomplete spec, a wrong assumption, or a scope change?
M|Lear|4. *|** If dv catches the same mistake from rj or mi twice, add it as a standing rv checkpoint in MEMORY.md
M|Lear|tx|5. **Never defend a bad decision.** If a previous architecture call was wrong, own it, log it, and fix it.
